{"tid":1367091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急呼籲 - 機場接機要用英文","createTime":"2019-07-26T07:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T09:50:11.000Z","uid":47289,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e1fc3c6bd57c858e48ce4ea2990aa3d052415b3a","tid":1367091,"uid":47289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:01:28.000Z","msg":"現況<br />\n睇Live post好多回覆話現場用緊廣東話<br />\n及<br />\n無大聲公用英文帶頭<br />\n<br />\n現況風險<br />\n外國人聽唔明廣東話，請主力用英文文宣，方可以達到目標:向外宣傳<br />\n及<br />\n現場未必上到網（收唔到建議）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\n準備出發或路上的人，如見字，請<br />\n1. 到場後宣揚用英文表達訴求<br />\n2. 帶任何擴音器並協助英文文宣"},{"pid":"faf30680893924f97bad9de908b9d5a4c3cb0531","tid":1367091,"uid":47289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:03:40.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e4dea1e85be261fe94379f8ec66e869e2b294197","tid":1367091,"uid":13349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:04:07.000Z","msg":"搵人舉牌叫旅客開airdrop<br />\n用＂Safety Alert in Hong Kong＂做主題<br />\n在場既人airdrop英文文宣"},{"pid":"b18d8ac65fd7af3cc908a33c2842116124d1bb9b","tid":1367091,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:04:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ec30a525ae4b316f1056f59b4eb521fdce05d43f","tid":1367091,"uid":47289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d0bf3d89233a98cd8803a128099561883a915525","tid":1367091,"uid":47289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:59:35.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3cd2398edd2b6616bd3c77a6a73eb1c6b929e09b","tid":1367091,"uid":47289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f97ab19538a87153e3130afcc0096b2df21298ea","tid":1367091,"uid":47289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6453a31199868a999603d6ff7cfa265aba5a4a54","tid":1367091,"uid":47289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"